{"tid":13560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我發覺呢度少咗一個風氣","createTime":"2016-11-30T06:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T06:43:51.000Z","uid":42653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d19334fe8c4023eb00e5ce39ceecb208ff68b20","tid":13560,"uid":42653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"就係郁d就話雞全部都係雞<br />\n<br />\n認真我對呢句說話好反感<br />\n<br />\n一次就好笑，兩次就微笑，第三次已經唔識笑<br />\n<br />\n嗰面好似9成有關女性嘅post都最後用呢句作總結<br />\n<br />\n真係驚心智唔成熟嘅小朋友以為係真，跟手仇視女性<br />\n<br />\n呢度會員真係高質d，so far都唔多覺好多人講，又好少見巴斯光年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗯，空氣仲清新咗"},{"pid":"2311ba3ac80728d411f385119581a8bfa4ede1b8","tid":13560,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:18:50.000Z","msg":"雞 全部都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7538e4c1be80c18cb139a7fc66de7b1a01d0318c","tid":13560,"uid":1685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:20:28.000Z","msg":"班範文撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<br />\n女post = 全部都係雞<br />\n<br />\n張繼聰post = 謝生 、陳生<br />\n<br />\n感情野 = 扮gay、互射<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多、成揪回覆有一半以上估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第1-2下覆果野襯個主題有時都幾好笑既、但太多就會悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e78f5ab3e6268705d06ef03d172d34daf45d93","tid":13560,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班範文撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<br />\n女post = 全部都係雞<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">謝</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: p